UAL Pilots Preparing New Buyout Bid: Officials of United Airlines' pilots union 
say they'll try to come up with a new buyout proposal for parent UAL Corp. by 
mid-week to prevent a costly recapitalization by the board. The union's 
governing council will meet Jan. 24 "to determine if we can develop a viable 
